{
  "stem": "27335.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we waited for the news from Hungary, what is happening in Hungary, and around Hungary, and in the whole-- whole-- whole-- operational field, how the war is going.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see that, or the battle, that was on-- went on in-- in Russia, dominance in the Soviet territories.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Hungary was-- Hungary was in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was hot stuff.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, the country next to Germany, it was Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because Hungary was fascist right, from 1919.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were placed, the two of us-- our group-- oh, by the way, our group-- no, there were only-- only-- only eight of us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because one failed at the other training in the camp, actually, so that there was eight of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But only-- only two of us were shipped from-- from England to-- to-- to Cairo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was one-- there was one who-- who dropped in from-- from-- from-- oh jeez, but we weren't sure.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was taken-- taken away just before Christmas, from England.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they told us that he disappeared some-- somewhere from over in Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had news only years later that he-- he-- he disappeared in-- over the Atlantic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somebody saw him in Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I met the Yugoslav Partisan comrade some 20 years back, in-- in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, well, he was-- he was with us there, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, we are three different places already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that's how it happened, to-- to some of the pieces.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just disappeared and goodbye for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- Well, we were then put into-- into a private house, just the two of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a-- we had an Arab-- an Egyptian Arab as a cook.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, he-- he looked after-- the housekeeper looked after us.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
